data.description: Hard to find property in Riverview! This single family home has a prime location near commuter routes but yet the natural setting under the towering mature oak trees is quiet and peaceful.  This 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage home was built in 2005 and has had interior and exterior updates by current owners that will delight you.  The roof was just redone in 2016 (county permit).  The interior features granite tops in kitchen and bathrooms.  The kitchen has ample cabinetry and stainless steel appliances to include oven, microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator.  Solid ¾ hardwood floors were installed in the main areas with modern ceramic flooring in kitchen, laundry and baths.  The master bedroom has an en suite bathroom with separate shower and soaking tub. The secondary bedrooms feature carpet and ceiling fans. Front and rear porches provide for entertaining and relaxing all year long. The HVAC is original but well-maintained. The .42 acre lot gives you the privacy you deserve with no HOA or CDD restrictions.  The 2 car garage allows for tons of storage and is also climate controlled for a great workspace.  There is a large workshop on the property with electric available that has a newer roof.  The property also features a carport structure, one wooden red storage shed and one small metal shed. Schedule your appointment to view today!
